---
title: Roasted Vegetable Quesadillas with Smoky Chipotle Mayo and Guacamole
description: In our book, quesadillas and guacamole are the ultimate comfort food. Stuffed with lightly caramelized asparagus, bell pepper, and onion, these whole-wheat quesadillas are both hearty and wholesome. A secret layer of chipotle mayo will forever change the way you make quesadillas.
